commit.message:
Makefile.in (stmt.o, [...]): Add missing dependency on bc-typecd.def.

* Makefile.in (stmt.o, expr.o, emit-rtl.o): Add missing dependency
on bc-typecd.def.
(bi-run.o): Fix formatting.

From-SVN: r5486
